        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            A letter to the airline from Connecticut’s attorney general cited ProPublica’s reporting on ICE Air flight attendants, who said it was unclear how shackled detainees would get off a plane in an emergency.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mac-funk">McKenzie Funk</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-04-25EDT05:00">April 25, 2025, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </span>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
            </div>
            </ol> <!-- end .most-read-group -->

</div> <!-- end .most-read -->

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

    
